Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.26,0:00:07.25,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,The best elements within us can spread light and virtue,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.25,0:00:09.88,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,and I know ponies who represent them all:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.29,0:00:11.33,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.33,0:00:12.47,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,bravery,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.47,0:00:13.40,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,healing,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.40,0:00:14.58,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,beauty,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.58,0:00:15.73,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,hope,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.73,0:00:16.84,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,and sorcery.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.02,0:00:22.72,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,Myself, and these Pillars of Equestria were gathered together by another
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.72,0:00:27.20,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,to maintain and share the light of these powerful ideals…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.65,0:00:31.96,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,But we soon came to believe the pony who brought us together,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.96,0:00:34.37,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,only wanted that power for himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.83,0:00:37.33,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,Cast out and alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.33,0:00:43.52,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,this power-mad pony turned to darkness to satisfy his thirst.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.52,0:00:48.47,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,Transformed into a Pony of Shadows, he returned for revenge
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.47,0:00:53.54,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,to extinguish the Pillars' light and rob the world of hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.54,0:00:58.18,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,To stop him, the Pillars and I must make a grave sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.01,0:01:01.67,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,But we shall leave behind a seed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.67,0:01:08.85,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,in hopes that one day it will grow into a force to stand against the darkness for all time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.85,0:01:11.68,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,We must now face the fiend
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.68,0:01:14.15,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,with the only plan we have…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.82,0:01:16.96,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,"…I only hope it will be enough."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.67,0:01:19.22,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,That's the last entry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.67,0:01:23.19,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,And maybe Starswirl's final words before he vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.57,0:02:05.36,Celestia,,0,0,0,,I've always wondered what happened to Starswirl.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.12,0:02:08.73,Celestia,,0,0,0,,This is quite a discovery, Sunburst.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:10.81,Twilight,,0,0,0,,So it's genuine?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.81,0:02:15.00,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You can verify that this journal really belonged to Starswirl the Bearded!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:16.64,Luna,,0,0,0,,Indeed. From the looks of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.64,0:02:19.92,Luna,,0,0,0,,the last thing he wrote before facing the Pony of Shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.40,0:02:25.02,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,So, the Pony of Shadows was really real?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.79,0:02:27.28,Celestia,,0,0,0,,It appears so.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.28,0:02:29.29,Luna,,0,0,0,,We never met the other Pillars,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.29,0:02:32.44,Luna,,0,0,0,,and we were too young to understand the danger they faced.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.44,0:02:34.00,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:36.89,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,All those legendary ponies were real too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.89,0:02:40.19,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,And they went out with Starswirl to face the Pony of Shadows?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.19,0:02:42.97,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,And then none of them were ever heard from again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.85,0:02:45.88,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Weren't you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.68,0:02:48.72,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,But what happened to them all?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.72,0:02:50.27,Rarity,,0,0,0,,They must have defeated the villain,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.27,0:02:52.89,Rarity,,0,0,0,,since Equestria is still full of light and hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.89,0:02:55.52,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,But how? And where did they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.52,0:02:57.53,Celestia,,0,0,0,,My Olde Ponish is a bit rusty,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.04,0:03:02.14,Celestia,,0,0,0,,but I wonder if the answers can be found somewhere within the pages of this book.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.76,0:03:06.33,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Well, I just happened to be an expert in Olde Ponish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.33,0:03:10.96,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I mean, I've practically memorized every ancient text about Starswirl there is…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.96,0:03:12.83,Spike,,0,0,0,,Seriously. All of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.34,0:03:15.80,Luna,,0,0,0,,We have fond memories of our old teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.80,0:03:19.56,Luna,,0,0,0,,If you could discover what happened to him, we would be most grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.07,0:03:24.11,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,Solving a thousand-year-old mystery could take forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.11,0:03:29.44,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,Think of the research, the re-reading, the re-re-reading…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.99,0:03:32.78,Celestia,,0,0,0,,You might find you need help.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.64,0:03:37.44,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Luckily, she's got a whole bushel of helpers right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.44,0:03:38.25,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Totally!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.39,0:03:42.67,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,How long will all this research take, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.20,0:03:45.10,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Let's get this back to my library.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.10,0:03:47.34,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm sure we'll figure out what happened in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:57.44,Spike,,0,0,0,,Figure it out yet, Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.56,0:04:03.15,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,Wha-what? What did you figure out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.68,0:04:04.96,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,You figured something out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.01,0:04:07.00,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.85,0:04:08.83,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.83,0:04:13.32,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I mean, Starswirl was a genius, obviously, but forget Olde Ponish,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.32,0:04:16.62,Twilight,,0,0,0,,there's parts where his hornwriting is like another language!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.59,0:04:23.79,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Twilight, we've been studyin', and referencin', and cross referencing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.79,0:04:25.79,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,for three days straight now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.92,0:04:31.71,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I haven't spent this much time reading since the last Daring Do book came out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.71,0:04:33.69,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Perhaps it is time to take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.69,0:04:36.83,Rarity,,0,0,0,,This mystery is over a thousand years old, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.83,0:04:38.94,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Another day or two won't make a difference!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.47,0:04:42.22,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Two days?! I don't want to waste two seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.20,0:04:46.52,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm close to an answer. I can feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.52,0:04:50.38,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,"Hearg sylfum se Ponhenge,"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.38,0:04:51.15,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.61,0:04:54.91,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The Temple of Ponhenge?! You can read that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.91,0:04:58.64,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,The hornwriting's pretty sloppy, but it's nowhere near as bad as mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.13,0:05:03.64,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,"Toward dol grimlic of fola firgenbeorg?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:07.23,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,At the base of Foal Mountain…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.90,0:05:10.14,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,"User endemest scield…"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.10,0:05:12.78,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Our last stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.16,0:05:18.84,Spike,,0,0,0,,Well, that sure sounds like a clue to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.88,0:05:31.76,Twilight,,0,0,0,,This is it. Ponhenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.44,0:05:33.72,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:41.02,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,I've never seen magical runes like these before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:42.01,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,Have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.12,0:05:50.00,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I don't think anypony's seen any of this for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.57,0:05:57.69,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,It'd take a whole team of ponies to clear away all this brush.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.60,0:06:04.56,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Even then, I'm not sure we'd find out what happened here a thousand years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.48,0:06:07.21,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.74,0:06:09.84,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I suppose it was a long shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.84,0:06:11.00,Spike,,0,0,0,,Cheer up, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.00,0:06:13.61,Spike,,0,0,0,,Finding a whole set of ancient ruins is pretty impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.38,0:06:16.08,Spike,,0,0,0,,Maybe you could write a paper on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.67,0:06:20.83,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I guess I hoped we'd get here and the mystery would just magically be explained.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.40,0:06:25.07,Spike,,0,0,0,,Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.68,0:06:37.40,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Starswirl!? I— I've wanted to meet you my whole life
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.40,0:06:39.40,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you're here…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.35,0:06:44.00,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,I don't think he is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.54,0:06:46.40,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,I don't think any of them are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.24,0:07:05.63,PonyOfShadows,,0,0,0,,You summon me at your peril, Starswirl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.63,0:07:10.28,PonyOfShadows,,0,0,0,,Once I defeat all of you, this realm will embrace the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:12.60,PonyOfShadows,,0,0,0,,as I did so long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:26.81,PonyOfShadows,,0,0,0,,Drawing me here will only make me stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.81,0:07:29.50,PonyOfShadows,,0,0,0,,You will never defeat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.50,0:07:32.03,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,We did not come here to defeat you…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.92,0:07:45.29,PonyOfShadows,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.64,0:07:48.41,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,We came to contain you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.87,0:08:06.67,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Well, you did ask for a magical explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.52,0:08:15.68,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.52,0:08:21.24,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,It looked like Starswirl cast a spell that banished the Pony of Shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.24,0:08:22.64,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:26.16,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,Powerful magic like that would leave an impression on this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.16,0:08:29.35,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,Bringing the book back here let us see what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.35,0:08:30.55,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Which was what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.01,0:08:35.70,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Starswirl and the rest of the Pillars sacrificed themselves to save Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.48,0:08:43.48,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,It's amazing to think one of the greatest mysteries of Equestria was solved with a musty old book from an antique shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.10,0:08:46.21,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,But I wouldn't say the mystery's solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.21,0:08:50.92,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,Starswirl's spell was one of the most powerful feats of magic in all of history.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.92,0:08:54.16,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,It'll take years of study before we fully understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.16,0:08:56.53,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I think I understand Starswirl's spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.88,0:09:01.49,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I know I've finished one of Starswirl's spells before
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.49,0:09:03.89,Twilight,,0,0,0,,but this one was on a whole different level!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.89,0:09:05.81,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Was it an explosion of magical feedback?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.81,0:09:07.84,Twilight,,0,0,0,,An evocation? A kind of incantation?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.84,0:09:10.26,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It's Starswirl, so the possibilities are endless!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.87,0:09:13.96,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And once Starlight set me on the right track with his crazy hornwriting…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.44,0:09:17.89,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I mean, he was a genius, so I guess we can forgive a little messiness…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.89,0:09:20.82,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I went through the journal again and it's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.27,0:09:23.28,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Twilight, darling,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.28,0:09:26.40,Rarity,,0,0,0,,we understand you're excited, but that's all we understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.00,0:09:28.88,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,What exactly is so amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.11,0:09:33.56,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Only how Starswirl and the other Pillars sent the Pony of Shadows to limbo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.56,0:09:34.88,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,They did what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:42.08,Twilight,,0,0,0,,They used their magic to open a portal between worlds, to limbo,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.08,0:09:44.12,Twilight,,0,0,0,,and pulled the Pony of Shadows inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.98,0:09:46.98,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Darling, your diorama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.98,0:09:47.88,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I made more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.39,0:09:55.30,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Starswirl thought the only way to trap the Pony of Shadows in limbo was for the Pillars to take him there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.30,0:09:57.81,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,So they got stuck too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.39,0:10:02.79,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,The Pony of Shadows must have been really awful for them to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.30,0:10:08.77,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,I suppose being trapped for all time with a super-duper bad guy in limbo might be okay if you were doing the limbo,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.30,0:10:10.55,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,but that's still pushing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.55,0:10:13.56,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The thing is, I think I can get them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.68,0:10:16.36,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,Twilight, are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.36,0:10:19.99,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,You can save the most legendary ponies of all time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.99,0:10:21.32,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.32,0:10:25.17,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Opening portals between worlds didn't work out well for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.91,0:10:27.27,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Are you sure it's safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.67,0:10:30.55,Twilight,,0,0,0,,First of all you opened portals through time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.55,0:10:33.59,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And second of all, Starswirl wrote the spell you used to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.59,0:10:35.59,Twilight,,0,0,0,,If he'd been here, he could have stopped it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.34,0:10:38.56,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Equestria will be safer with him in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.56,0:10:39.97,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We have to save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.37,0:10:43.04,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,But you'd be savin' all the Pillars, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.44,0:10:45.33,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,And they disappeared ages ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.05,0:10:47.62,Twilight,,0,0,0,,That's the thing about limbo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.62,0:10:49.41,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It isn't one place or another.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.41,0:10:52.05,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It's in between, so time stands still.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.05,0:10:54.69,Twilight,,0,0,0,,If we can pull them out, it'll be like they never left.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.69,0:10:57.00,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I actually built another model to demonstra…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.68,0:10:59.83,Spike,,0,0,0,,What can we do to help?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.08,0:11:04.28,Twilight,,0,0,0,,If I'm right, we need to find items that are connected to the Pillars in some way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.28,0:11:07.30,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You mean, like, stuff that belonged to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.30,0:11:10.47,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,How would we know what to look for? Or where?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.22,0:11:14.07,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Luckily, Starswirl took a lot of notes…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.84,0:11:20.45,Twilight,,0,0,0,,…my compatriots are as varied as the realm itself and hail from every corner of our land,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.45,0:11:24.12,Twilight,,0,0,0,,bringing with them artifacts and talismans of great power…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.84,0:11:26.84,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Twilight, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.94,0:11:29.38,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm not doing anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.12,0:11:32.39,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Rockhoof's shovel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.82,0:11:34.77,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Flash Magnus' shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.25,0:11:37.00,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Mistmane's flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:38.93,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Meadowbrook's mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.17,0:11:43.30,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,And the blindfold Somnambula wore when she faced that nasty sphinx!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.01,0:11:47.54,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I guess we don't need to figure out who should get what.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.46,0:11:56.29,Petunia,,0,0,0,,Professor! It's a Mighty Helm headpiece!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.29,0:11:58.79,Petunia,,0,0,0,,Maybe it belonged to Rockhoof himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.33,0:12:04.50,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Legends don't wear helmets. This belonged to a real pony.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.50,0:12:08.50,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Oh, I can guarantee Rockhoof was as real as you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.47,0:12:18.20,Somepony,,0,0,0,,And I suppose that ravine was dug with his trusty shovel to save the village from an erupting volcano.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.20,0:12:18.80,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.46,0:12:22.55,Somepony,,0,0,0,,I love old legends as much as anypony,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.55,0:12:29.19,Somepony,,0,0,0,,but a pony strong enough to save a village from rushing lava with a shovel is preposterous!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.76,0:12:46.32,Somepony,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you just did that. You saved us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.32,0:12:52.21,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I bet if you told somepony else the story it might sound preposterous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.58,0:13:02.13,Somepony,,0,0,0,,I suppose some stories might be true…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.14,0:13:08.00,Somepony,,0,0,0,,And Rockhoof's appears to be one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.00,0:13:22.88,Somepony,,0,0,0,,You keep those hooves to yourself, dearie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.27,0:13:26.85,Somepony,,0,0,0,,This place has been in my family for generations,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.85,0:13:31.84,Somepony,,0,0,0,,and I'm not about to let some whippersnapper take the last good piece of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.31,0:13:36.56,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Time was, ponies came from far and wide to see these gardens.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:40.61,Somepony,,0,0,0,,But that flower's the only worthwhile thing left.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.94,0:14:01.04,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Perhaps it just seemed like your gardens were worthless,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.04,0:14:03.60,Rarity,,0,0,0,,but a little pruning can work wonders.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.58,0:14:07.86,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Of course you will have to look after more than just one flower now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.66,0:14:12.69,Somepony,,0,0,0,,You've given me back my family's legacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.27,0:14:17.32,Somepony,,0,0,0,,The flower you wanted seems like a fair trade for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.93,0:14:25.43,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I can't believe Flash Magnus' shield ended up in the Dragon Lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.04,0:14:31.88,Spike,,0,0,0,,Good thing you brought the Official Equestrian Friendship Ambassador To The Dragons to help you navigate our customs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.88,0:14:34.69,Spike,,0,0,0,,Like our favorite sport — gorge surfing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.79,0:14:48.02,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Okay. That was awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.01,0:14:52.77,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Dragon Lord Ember commanded us to make peace with ponies,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.77,0:14:55.59,Somepony,,0,0,0,,but it doesn't mean you can surf in our spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.96,0:15:01.88,Spike,,0,0,0,,Fellas. As the Official Equestrian Friendship Ambassador To The Dragons
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.88,0:15:04.56,Spike,,0,0,0,,I have to say, that's not very friendly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.56,0:15:06.34,Garble,,0,0,0,,Well, what do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.82,0:15:11.36,Garble,,0,0,0,,The puny, pony dragon's sticking up for his pony pal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.84,0:15:15.28,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Hey! That's an ancient pony artifact.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.21,0:15:18.05,Garble,,0,0,0,,Hooves off my gorge board!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.05,0:15:21.56,Garble,,0,0,0,,I found it in the desert and finders keepers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.56,0:15:23.75,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,It isn't yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.42,0:15:25.75,Garble,,0,0,0,,It sure looks like mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.02,0:15:29.38,Garble,,0,0,0,,But, I might consider racing you for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.96,0:15:30.85,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.61,0:15:35.19,Garble,,0,0,0,,No. I mean you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.36,0:15:40.64,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.46,0:15:48.84,Somepony,,0,0,0,,On your marks…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.84,0:15:49.96,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Get set…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.96,0:15:51.04,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Surf!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.15,0:16:07.00,Spike,,0,0,0,,I won?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.00,0:16:07.78,Spike,,0,0,0,,I won!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.95,0:16:10.76,Spike,,0,0,0,,Give up the shield, Garble.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.02,0:16:15.67,Garble,,0,0,0,,Lord Ember only commanded us to be nice to ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.67,0:16:20.56,Garble,,0,0,0,,She never said anything about pony-loving dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.84,0:16:32.64,Spike,,0,0,0,,Since Dragon Lord Ember commanded you to make peace with ponies, you can't very well attack one of their friends, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.98,0:16:35.48,Garble,,0,0,0,,I guess we'll find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.38,0:16:45.28,Garble,,0,0,0,,Why is he always hiding behind ponies?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.28,0:16:47.72,Spike,,0,0,0,,I wasn't hiding when I beat you down the ridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.46,0:16:49.16,Garble,,0,0,0,,You fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.79,0:16:55.10,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Wow, you must be slow, if all Spike had to do to win was fall down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.10,0:16:56.75,Garble,,0,0,0,,I'm faster than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.75,0:16:57.53,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Doubt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.53,0:16:58.35,Garble,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.35,0:17:00.03,Garble,,0,0,0,,I'll race you back to the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.03,0:17:02.51,Garble,,0,0,0,,If you win, you can have your pony junk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.16,0:17:07.84,Garble,,0,0,0,,But if I win, you'll leave and I get to give it to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.84,0:17:11.08,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Fine. I'm pretty sure I could beat you anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.08,0:17:15.42,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,but with that heavy hunk of metal on your back, it'll be a snap.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.27,0:17:17.96,Garble,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah. Thanks for the tip.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.89,0:17:20.86,Garble,,0,0,0,,See ya at the top, loser!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.54,0:17:29.08,Garble,,0,0,0,,Hey! That's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.08,0:17:31.60,Spike,,0,0,0,,Finders keepers, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.59,0:17:35.90,SomeponyOrange,,0,0,0,,See, because that's what you said to them when they first showed up…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.96,0:17:47.20,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Just remember not to turn away from them, Cattail.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.20,0:17:49.93,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Flash bees can get pretty aggressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.93,0:17:53.05,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I guess that's why none of the other bayou animals can get to the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.62,0:17:58.38,SomeponyOrange,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it make more sense for you to wear the mask that calms the bees?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.86,0:18:00.08,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,It would…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.39,0:18:03.58,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,…if I didn't have to fly up here to move their hive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.61,0:18:06.27,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.99,0:18:15.21,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Now the other bayou creatures can get to the water without the bees feeling threatened.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.27,0:18:18.84,SomeponyOrange,,0,0,0,,You know, you didn't have to help with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.84,0:18:21.36,Somepony,,0,0,0,,I would've lent you the mask anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.36,0:18:22.27,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.96,0:18:24.78,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,But I couldn't leave without helping.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.97,0:18:29.47,Somepony,,0,0,0,,I don't think anypony can find anything in there
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.20,0:18:32.25,DaringDo,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't give up hope just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.99,0:18:41.07,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,This old blindfold was stuck in the drain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.60,0:18:43.66,DaringDo,,0,0,0,,Weren't you looking for a blindfold?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.66,0:18:44.75,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.36,0:18:52.27,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I'm going to meet Starswirl the Bearded…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.27,0:18:54.11,Twilight,,0,0,0,,you know, outside of my dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.11,0:18:56.65,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you're actually going through with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.65,0:18:57.63,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.56,0:19:01.02,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,I'm all for pushing the envelope, obviously,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.02,0:19:03.31,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,but this is pretty out there for you, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.69,0:19:07.85,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,What's "out there" about saving the most legendary ponies of all time
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.85,0:19:09.55,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,from a thousands year-old prison?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.09,0:19:12.70,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Well, nothing when you say it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.56,0:19:17.60,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,Unless… "the most legendary ponies of all time" knew what they were doing,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.60,0:19:19.16,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,and we shouldn't mess with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.79,0:19:23.77,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Starswirl and the Pillars did the best they could back then,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.77,0:19:28.30,Sunburst,,0,0,0,,but magic has come a long way — mostly because of the work they did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:33.04,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,That's true. And you did get your wings from finishing one of Starswirl's spells…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.96,0:19:34.81,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.06,0:19:41.36,StarlightGlimmer,,0,0,0,,But, then I messed with one and nearly destroyed the universe, so…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.36,0:19:45.61,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Starlight, Starswirl the Bearded is the greatest wizard who ever lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.61,0:19:48.91,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The chance to have him back in Equestria is worth the risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.91,0:19:50.49,Spike,,0,0,0,,That's good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.49,0:19:54.17,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, we'd have brought this shield for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.17,0:19:57.18,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I hope you don't think you're the only one to find her artifact,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.18,0:20:00.00,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,because this here shovel says otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.52,0:20:02.83,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Honestly, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.83,0:20:04.99,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Not everything is a competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.99,0:20:09.68,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Buuut Mistmane's flower is by far the most attractive of the artifacts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.68,0:20:14.75,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,You're just saying that because you didn't have to scuba dive in a pit of green slime to get yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.75,0:20:16.88,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Or move a Flash Bee hive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.44,0:20:18.57,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Good work everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.46,0:20:21.93,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.79,0:20:45.84,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,What… What has happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.81,0:20:49.42,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It worked! We brought you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.42,0:20:50.62,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,To where?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.62,0:20:54.19,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You and the others have been trapped in limbo for a thousand years,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.19,0:20:56.03,Twilight,,0,0,0,,but I figured out how to get you ho…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.03,0:20:58.27,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,What!? No, no, no, no…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.27,0:21:00.60,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,You must undo what you've done!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.60,0:21:04.35,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What? Why? I mean, I don't think I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.35,0:21:06.59,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,You cannot bring us back…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.59,0:21:09.36,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But I did. I brought all the Pillars back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.36,0:21:12.41,Starswirl,,0,0,0,,You cannot bring only the Pillars back…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.46,0:21:29.32,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh, no…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.96,0:21:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,TO BE PONTINUED……
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.96,0:21:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,anon2anon\Nsunnysubs.com
